<%- include('./partials/header') %>

    <body>
        <%- include('./partials/menu', { activePage: 'questions' , pageType: 'main' }) %>
            <main class="content-area">
                <div class="container-fluid px-2 px-md-4">
                    <div class="row g-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-lg-9">
                            <section class="mb-4">
                                <h1 class="h3 fw-normal mb-2">Ask Your Question</h1>
                                <p class="text-secondary">Make sure your question is clear and provides enough
                                    information for our community to help</p>
                            </section>

                            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <form>
                                        <div class="mb-4 pb-4 border-bottom">
                                            <label for="title" class="form-label fw-500">Title <span class="mandatory">*</span></label>
                                            <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-lg" id="title"
                                                placeholder="What's your programming problem? Be specific." value="">
                                            <ul class="text-secondary d-block mt-2 me-0">
                                                <li>Pretend you're talking to a busy colleague. Avoid special characters
                                                </li>
                                                <li>Be specific and imagine you're asking a question to another person
                                                </li>
                                                <li>Good: "Why does PHP_EOL not work when I use the file_get_contents()
                                                    to write a file?"</li>
                                                <li>Bad: "PHP writing to files"</li>
                                            </ul>
                                            <div class="text-secondary small mt-2">Character count: <span
                                                    id="titleCount">0</span>/150</div>
                                        </div>

                                        <div class="mb-4 pb-4 border-bottom">
                                            <label for="body" class="form-label fw-500">Description <span class="mandatory">*</span></label>
                                            <textarea class="form-control" id="body" rows="12" placeholder="Walk us through your problem.

- When did the problem start?
- What have you already tried?
- What did you expect to happen?
- What actually happened?

Include relevant code snippets when possible."></textarea>

                                            <div class="alert alert-warning small mt-3 mb-3">
                                                <strong>Tip:</strong> Use code formatting by wrapping it in three
                                                backticks (```). You can also use <strong>markdown</strong> for
                                                formatting.
                                            </div>

                                            <div style="background: #f4f5f6; padding: 12px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px;"
                                                id="preview">
                                                <small class="text-secondary">Preview:</small>
                                                <div id="previewContent" style="margin-top: 8px;"></div>
                                            </div>

                                            <small class="text-secondary d-block mt-2">
                                                • Explain what you've already tried and what didn't work. Include error
                                                messages
                                                • Share code examples. Use the toolbar above or wrap in triple backticks
                                                (```)
                                                • People will be happier if you paste actual code snippets
                                            </small>
                                        </div>

                                        <div class="mb-4 pb-4 border-bottom">
                                            <label for="tags" class="form-label fw-500">Tags <span class="mandatory">*</span></label>
                                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="tags"
                                                placeholder="e.g. javascript react css" value="">
                                            <small class="text-secondary d-block mt-2">
                                                • Add up to 5 tags to describe what your question is about
                                                • Each tag must start with a letter or number, lowercase, max 35
                                                characters
                                                • Press Enter or Space to add a tag
                                                • Tags help us make sure your question gets seen by the right people
                                            </small>

                                            <!-- Tag Display -->
                                            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3" id="tagsList">
                                                <!-- Tags will be added here dynamically -->
                                            </div>
                                        </div>

                                        <div class="mb-4 pb-4 border-bottom">
                                            <div class="form-check mb-3">
                                                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="hasAttempted">
                                                <label class="form-check-label" for="hasAttempted">
                                                    <strong>I've already done my research <span class="mandatory">*</span></strong>
                                                    <p class="text-secondary small mb-0">I've searched for similar
                                                        questions and haven't found a solution</p>
                                                </label>
                                            </div>

                                            <div class="form-check mb-3">
                                                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="isMinimal">
                                                <label class="form-check-label" for="isMinimal">
                                                    <strong>I can provide a minimal reproducible example <span class="mandatory">*</span></strong>
                                                    <p class="text-secondary small mb-0">My example is complete and can
                                                        be run to reproduce the issue</p>
                                                </label>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>

                                        <!-- Help Text -->
                                        <div class="alert alert-light border mb-4">
                                            <h6 class="mb-2">Before publishing, please read:</h6>
                                            <ul class="small mb-0 ps-3">
                                                <li>Are you asking for help debugging code, or recommending a tool?</li>
                                                <li>Is your question about a specific technology (JavaScript, Python,
                                                    etc.)?</li>
                                                <li>Is there an existing question that answers your question?</li>
                                                <li>Are you looking for debugging help? Include an error message or
                                                    describe the unexpected behavior</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>

                                        <!-- Buttons -->
                                        <div class="d-flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Publish Your Question</button>
                                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-danger"
                                                onclick="window.history.back()">Discard</button>
                                        </div>
                                    </form>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Sidebar Help -->
                        <div class="col-12 col-lg-3">
                            <!-- How to Ask -->
                            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h6 class="card-title mb-3">How to Ask</h6>
                                    <ul class="list-unstyled small">
                                        <li class="mb-2">
                                            <strong>Be specific</strong><br>
                                            <span class="text-secondary">Describe the problem clearly and
                                                concisely</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mb-2">
                                            <strong>Show your research</strong><br>
                                            <span class="text-secondary">Tell us what you've already tried</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mb-2">
                                            <strong>Include code</strong><br>
                                            <span class="text-secondary">Provide a minimal example</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <strong>Use formatting</strong><br>
                                            <span class="text-secondary">Make your question easy to read</span>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- What to Avoid -->
                            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h6 class="card-title mb-3">Avoid</h6>
                                    <ul class="list-unstyled small">
                                        <li class="mb-2">
                                            <span class="text-danger"><i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i></span> Ask multiple unrelated questions
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mb-2">
                                            <span class="text-danger"><i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i></span> Demanding an answer ("URGENT!!!")
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mb-2">
                                            <span class="text-danger"><i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i></span> Asking for debugging of thousands of lines
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mb-2">
                                            <span class="text-danger"><i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i></span> Asking for external resources/tools recommendations
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <span class="text-danger"><i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i></span> Using special characters or ALL CAPS
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h6 class="card-title mb-3">Helpful Resources</h6>
                                    <ul class="list-unstyled small">
                                        <li class="mb-2">
                                            <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none">How to ask good questions</a>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mb-2">
                                            <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none">Text Formatting Guidelines</a>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mb-2">
                                            <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none">What topics can I ask about
                                                here?</a>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none">My question was marked as
                                                duplicate</a>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </main>

            <script src="/js/newQuestions.js"></script>

    </body>

    <%- include('./partials/footer') %>